Rating: 4
I used basmati rice and cut the mustard seeds in half. I kept the heat quite low when toasting the mustard seeds. It seemed to help the popping out of the pan! The basmati rice was very flavorful. It made an excellent accompaniment to the "Spiced Roast Chicken Breast". My family (kids 5,7,9) and friends love this meal! The spices in the chicken are very distinct but not overwhelming to the taste buds.

Rating: 4
