Rating: 4
This is a wonderful rice dish. I served it with the Spiced Chicken Breasts as suggested by Gourmet and it was a really nice combination. However, I also served it with lightly sauteed salmon filets and thought it went much better with that. The yield is greater than the recipe indicates and I ended up with a lot of left over rice. This reheats well, the flavor does not become any more or less intense. This recipe provides a really nice alternative to plain steamed rice or rice pilaf.